Andvari Shadowmist<br>
TWC</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#242422><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/utelivaksk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TelivakSK</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#DDA0DD>4/30/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#DDA0DD>11:54:44 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: SARYRN PVP TOURNAMENT - please read</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">And:<br>
<br>
When I say twink, I more or less consider anyone under the level of 40 who has gears that are well beyond the capability of that person to get.  At level 40-45, if a character have kunark armor, well, it's not inconcievable though uncommon.  But a level 30 with full class/kunark armor, 10k belt, and expensive weapon, well, that's a bit hard to not be qualified a twink.  Correct me if I'm wrong but I think armor and weapons makes more of a difference at lower level?  Shrugs, I've got a level 34 Paladin right now with close to 700 ac, hits for 30-60's and I can still solo blues easily and the occasional white without needing LoH.  That was something Telivak could never do back when he was in 30s.  Well, except fear kiting but then that's the one distinct advantage SKs have.  Anyways, I dunno just how much of a difference twinking makes in terms of PVP but I'm sure there is a good deal of advantage or people wouldn't be bothering to twink.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntaverncommonsroom.showMessage?topicID=1717.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntaverncommonsroom.showMessage?topicID=1707.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95% BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntaverncommonsroom.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1715.topic&index=6><IMG SRC=http://home.earthlink.net/~jerrigaither/Saryrn/Reply.jpg border=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntaverncommonsroom.emailToFriend?topicID=1715.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/images/email.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Email This To a Friend"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;Email This To a Friend</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntaverncommonsroom.threadControl?topicID=1715.topic><IMG SRC=